{"issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/6917", "repo": "rails", "body": "@headius: I chose to expose all of the CHM's tuning settings via `ThreadSafe::Cache`'s [initialiser](https://github.com/headius/thread_safe/blob/6c53370f3f7c31b8841991129cdcf516dad2cb57/lib/thread_safe/cache.rb#L82-L92).\n\nI'm also defining a 1-way, low-memory (though `:initial_capacity => 1` might be just a bit too conservative) [subclass](https://github.com/thedarkone/rails/commit/8eebc33e7ea515bc12275e03acf66facea12db4e#L2R7) that ends up being used for all but 2 of the Rails caches.\n\nI'm on European time, but I'll try to show on IRC tomorrow.", "_id": {"$oid": "523801f5bd3543c15100c22e"}, "issue_id": 6917, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/6697789", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/6917#issuecomment-6697789", "updated_at": "2012-07-01T22:48:01Z", "user": {"subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thedarkone/subscriptions", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thedarkone/events{/privacy}", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thedarkone/repos", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thedarkone/gists{/gist_id}", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/thedarkone", "login": "thedarkone", "gravatar_id": "c203190318ed9534390c93d1744a6cf1", "html_url": "https://github.com/thedarkone", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thedarkone/following{/other_user}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thedarkone/received_events", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thedarkone/orgs", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/c203190318ed9534390c93d1744a6cf1?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F68e4593563e1b425a7717504bca103d6.png", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thedarkone/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "id": 15688, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thedarkone/followers", "type": "User"}, "created_at": "2012-07-01T22:48:01Z", "id": 6697789, "own